name: 2025 The 8th International Conference on Software Engineering and Information Management
content: Publication: Submitted papers will be Peer-Reviewed (Double Blind) and the accepted ones will be collected in the conference proceedings to be published with International Conference Proceedings by ACM (ISBN: 979-8-4007-1043-8), which indexed in Ei Compendex, Scopus, CPCI, IET etc. major databases.
organizers: University of Electronic Science and Technology of China, China; Singapore Institute of Electronics
